  "contenu": [
    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "<p>Soit la fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f=\\frac{1}{3}\\textbf{1}_{[-1;2]}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Vérifier que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> définit une densité de probabilité.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>On vérifie que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est une fonction positive et son intégrale vaut <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\int_{-\\infty}^{+\\infty}f(x)dx = \\int_{-1}^{2} \\frac{1}{3}dx = 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\PP(1 \\leq X \\leq 3) = \\int_1^3 \\frac{1}{3} \\textbf{1}_{[-1;2]} dx = \\frac{1}{3} \\int_1^2 dx = \\frac{1}{3}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}